revision.text:
{{draft}}

[[{{PAGENAME}}]] is a {{ill|Kotohira Shrines|lt=Kotohira Shrine|ja|金刀比羅神社}} located in {{ill|Japan|simple}}. It worships {{ill|Konpira Gongen|simple}}.


{{ill|Kotohira Shrines|ja|金刀比羅神社}} are [[shinto shrine]]s dedicated to [[Ōmononushi]]. Due to [[Shinbutsu-shūgō]] they often also worship [[Konpira Gongen]]

They are part of the famous Inahachikonten Shrines (稲八金天神社)  of the [[Shrine Consolidation Policy]] alongside [[Inari Shrine]], [[Hachiman Shrine]], {{ill|Kotohira Shrines|ja|金刀比羅神社}}, and [[Tenmangū|Tenmangu Shrine]].

