'''Kotohira Ōtori Shrine''' (金刀比羅・大鷲神社) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinto shrine|qq=}} located in {{ill|Magane Town|ja|真金町|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Magane Town|qq=}}, {{ill|Minami-ku (Yokohama)|ja|南区 (横浜市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minami-ku (Yokohama)|qq=}}, {{ill|Yokohama|ja|横浜市|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokohama|qq=}}, {{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanagawa Prefecture|qq=}}. It is a former {{ill|Unranked Shrine|ja|無格社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Unranked Shrine|qq=}}. The registered name as a religious corporation is '''Religious Corporation Kotohira Shrine''' (宗教法人金刀比羅神社). The shrine grounds also include a subordinate shrine dedicated to {{ill|Fushimi Inari Shrine|ja|伏見稲荷神社|1=Fushimi Inari-taisha|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fushimi Inari Shrine|13=User:Immanuelle/Fushimi Inari-taisha|qq=}}.

